41 A report so approved shall be signed by the chairperson of the committee and filed with
42 the Clerk of the House of Representatives.
43 (D) In the absence of an approved report, the chairperson may file with the Clerk of the
44 House of Representatives a copy of the minutes of the meetings of the committee in lieu
45 thereof.
46 (E) The report shall be filed with the Clerk of the House of Representatives by January
47 14, 2026.
48 (7) Abolishment. The committee shall stand abolished on December 31, 2025.
